{"tid":1590283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動po］929 10.1 全人類做舉旗撚 再開","createTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T01:39:23.000Z","uid":243666,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1ed11de94deebfdad535418d5baa48257c2866","tid":1590283,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.29要爭取國際focus</span><br />\n呢排國際傳媒日日報打架報到悶<br />\n所以我哋要做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">舉旗撚</span></span><br />\n個畫面好睇 而且有新鮮感<br />\n舉旗人數要夠多 最好超過10萬人 <br />\n而我哋要舉返<span style=\"color: gold;\">自己嘅旗</span> 如 黑色區旗/自由鳥<br />\n<br />\n第一 自己嘅旗有歸屬感 凝聚翻香港人<br />\n<br />\n第二 手足為香港而戰並非其他國家<br />\n所以9.29舉美國舉略有不妥<br />\n<br />\n第三 多次舉美國旗會引起外國人反感<br />\n<br />\n另外 格離post話有日本人想幫手<br />\n我建議9.29夾埋日本 台灣 組織一次全球反共大遊行<br />\n<br />\n日本手足post<br />\n【929】日本手足想幫手，你唔係唔理呀嘛？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589915\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589915</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紙旗就得 最緊要多</span></span><br />\n<br />\n和理非同我一人舉一支黑旗<br />\n黑衫，黑旗，賀佢國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大量template任你揀<br />\n請瘋狂印，通街掛，一人一黑旗，人人揸旗行街<br />\n好期待中共國慶，而全港掛滿黑旗嘅畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jgVqj3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jgVqj3.png&h=24bf0985&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/235117_55edb87cb0108100bde7fd3a9bae60e0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F235117_55edb87cb0108100bde7fd3a9bae60e0.png&h=a7c07e8d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/235117_e29207ac7d5fc37f41786062d5078afc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F235117_e29207ac7d5fc37f41786062d5078afc.png&h=b34799c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/235118_7c83a8972f6fe9fc71e588f94ee7e25e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F235118_7c83a8972f6fe9fc71e588f94ee7e25e.png&h=e712b70a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/235118_a621bebe1f3bbcc8d55bbe112d65494c.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F235118_a621bebe1f3bbcc8d55bbe112d65494c.jpeg&h=c4028a3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/235119_0742925cbf8968214a25026ce3958c5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F235119_0742925cbf8968214a25026ce3958c5b.png&h=713b3adc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/23/235306_ac83d710d6b7f9f25d971200b889dcf8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2F235306_ac83d710d6b7f9f25d971200b889dcf8.png&h=0ce340d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5653146e0fa4f1d697d413edc26964eb99715a7","tid":1590283,"uid":243666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"272f9c6cfe0f01ece20aea8255f58e342534b927","tid":1590283,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"p